Sayonara no Kawari ni 2013: Official music video for idol group Oha Girl Chu! Chu! Chu!'s song Sayonara no Kawari ni 2013. It is a cover of a song titled Sayonara no Kawari ni performed by the idol group Oha Ska in 2000 by the 1999 cast of Oha Suta, a Japanese children's TV show. Both idol groups are owned by the Oha Suta franchise.
